{"id": "22954", "post": "<div class=\"post-22954 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-community-news tag-easy-vpn tag-proxy tag-proxy-setup tag-security tag-tutorial tag-vpn tag-vpn-setup tag-wireguard tag-wireguard-install\" id=\"post-22954\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/community-news-wireguard-install-released-for-easy-vpn-setup-and-configuration/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Community News: WireGuard-install released for easy VPN setup and configuration</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/community-news/\" rel=\"tag\">community news</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/easy-vpn/\" rel=\"tag\">easy vpn</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/proxy/\" rel=\"tag\">proxy</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/proxy-setup/\" rel=\"tag\">proxy setup</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/security/\" rel=\"tag\">Security</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/tutorial/\" rel=\"tag\">tutorial</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/vpn/\" rel=\"tag\">vpn</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/vpn-setup/\" rel=\"tag\">vpn setup</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/wireguard/\" rel=\"tag\">wireguard</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/wireguard-install/\" rel=\"tag\">wireguard-install</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> June 6, 2020 @ 2:12 am, by Jon Biloh</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Interesting-Industry-News-LEB.jpg.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Interesting-Industry-News-LEB.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"416\" height=\"245\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></a></p><p>In May we asked our readers and community members to <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/looking-for-community-industry-news/\">submit note worthy news</a> that can be featured on LowEndBox. We got tons of feedback and we\u2019re excited to start sharing all the news over the next couple months (and hopefully longer).</p><p>Today we are thrilled to be able to share our first community news tidbit about \u201cWireGuard-install\u201d the easy to use tool to help you setup your own private VPN, released by community member <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/profile/Nyr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@Nyr</a>. Over on LowEndTalk <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/profile/Nyr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@Nyr</a> has been a trusted member since 2011 (making him one of the very first users on LowEndTalk).</p><p>If you are looking to easily setup your own VPN/Proxy you should absolutely give \u201cWireGuard-install\u201d a look to save you time and provide peace of mind. If you need a cheap KVM VPS to host your VPN/Proxy on, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/kvm/\">we can help you with that, too</a>.</p><p>About \u201cWireGuard-install\u201d</p><blockquote><p>For those readers who would like to quickly get their own VPN server up and running, community member Nyr has released a new tool named wireguard-install.</p><p>This tool takes care of the installation and configuration of a WireGuard server on any of the popular Linux distributions such as Ubuntu, Debian, CentOS, and Fedora. The user is only asked to provide few details like a name for the VPN client or which DNS provider should be used while the rest of the necessary work to install WireGuard and configure the networking and firewall is performed automatically by the installer.</p><p>At the end of the installation, the configuration file is provided ready-to-use in a WireGuard client, plus a QR configuration code that can be scanned to easily configure a smartphone. Upon installation completion, the script also provides functionality to add new users or manage existing ones.</p><p>This open-source project is a continuation of Nyr\u2019s OpenVPN installer, which is already popular among our community members and has been supported for almost a decade.</p></blockquote><p>Links:<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Nyr/wireguard-install\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://github.com/Nyr/wireguard-install</a>&nbsp;(the WireGuard installer)<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Nyr/openvpn-install\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://github.com/Nyr/openvpn-install</a>&nbsp;(the OpenVPN installer)</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/wireguard-screenshot.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22955 litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/wireguard-screenshot.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"629\" height=\"376\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/wireguard-screenshot.png 629w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/wireguard-screenshot-300x179.png.webp 300w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 629px) 100vw, 629px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 629px) 100vw, 629px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/wireguard-screenshot.png 629w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/wireguard-screenshot-300x179.png.webp 300w\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></p><p>If you try \u201cWireGuard-install\u201d let us know about your experience and a big thanks to <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/profile/Nyr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@Nyr</a>.</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape